Lewis (amụrụ n'April 18, 1971), nke a maara dị ka Spliff Star, bụ ónyé America na-eti egwu na ónyé na-emepụta ihe na Flatbush, Brooklyn, New York. A maara ya nke ọma màkà ọrụ ya na Busta Rhymes. Ma Vibe na Complex depụtara Spliff Star dị ka otu n'ime ndị ikom kachasị mma na hip hop.
Ọ bụbu ónyé otu Flipmode Squad
O guzobere akara nke ya, PaperRock Records na 2007, wee wepụta mgbalị mbụ ya n'onwe ya na 2008
